---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ProjectShowcase from '../components/ProjectShowcase.jsx';
---

<Layout 
  title="Projects & Tenders | Shivay Construction Company"
  description="Explore our completed and ongoing railway infrastructure tenders including OHE works, track layouts, and bridge constructions."
>
  <!-- Projects Hero -->
  <section class="projects-hero section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <span class="hero-badge">Project Showcase</span>
      <h1>Our Tender Executions</h1>
      <p style="margin: 1.5rem auto 0; max-width: 75ch;">
        Shivay Construction Company takes pride in successfully executing major public sector tenders. Review our track record of railway electrification, civil work, and signaling projects across Indian Railways divisions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Interactive Project Showcase Section -->
  <section class="portfolio-section section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <ProjectShowcase client:load />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JV & Subcontracting Info -->
  <section class="jv-info-section section">
    <div class="container grid-2">
      <div class="jv-text">
        <h2 class="heading-accent">Joint Ventures & Subcontracting</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          To qualify for high-capital Indian Railways projects, we frequently form Joint Ventures (JV) with experienced engineering consultancies, consortiums, and technology partners. We bring extensive localized execution capability, Class-A contractor credentials, and equipment capacity.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you are an EPC company looking for a reliable, field-tested railway contractor in the North Central or Eastern divisions to execute parts of your larger award, contact our business development desk.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="tender-portals-card card">
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3>E-Tendering Credentials</h3>
          <ul class="credentials-list">
            <li>
              <span class="cred-dot"></span>
              <strong>IREPS ID:</strong> Verified bidder for Indian Railways e-Procurement System.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="cred-dot"></span>
              <strong>GeM Portal:</strong> Registered service provider on Government e-Marketplace.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="cred-dot"></span>
              <strong>RDSO:</strong> Compliant with Research Designs and Standards Organisation requirements.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="cred-dot"></span>
              <strong>PAN-India:</strong> Eligible to bid for Zonal Railways, Metro Rails, and DFCCIL tenders.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .projects-hero {
    padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 3rem);
    background: radial-gradient(circle at bottom, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .portfolio-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
  }

  .jv-info-section {
    align-items: center;
  }

  .tender-portals-card {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--amber);
  }

  .tender-portals-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .credentials-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .credentials-list li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .cred-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--accent);
    margin-top: 8px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .jv-info-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
